the company CAN use a hybrid cloud for cloudifying ,
private cloud and third-party, public cloud services.
Banking data MUST be kept on premise only since it's not secure over the cloud.
Healthcare, transport data can be stored over the cloud.

Since the company is growing and have a revenue of 18%, it's better if the company moves the infrastructure to cloud,
reducing the costs, virtualizing and giving more computing power.
The company can use cloud services like  Microsoft Azure, AWS cloud .
